OL,3,CTeaching unions in Northern Ireland
OL,4,Caccept 4% pay rise
OL,6,FUnions representing teachers across
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland have accepted a pay
OL,8,Frise of 4% for 2025-26.
OL,10,FSome 87% of NASUWT members voted in
OL,11,Ffavour of the consolidated cost-of-
OL,12,Fliving pay award that will be
OL,13,Fbackdated to September 1 2025.
OL,15,FThe union's leaders said their focus
OL,16,Fwill now shift to reducing teachers'
OL,17,F"excessive workload".
