OL,7,Fthe decision and said he will respond
OL,8,Fto the Independent Review on Teacher
OL,9,FWorkload within the coming weeks.
OL,11,FIn April last year, the Northern
OL,12,FIreland Teachers' Council (NITC),
OL,13,Fwhich represents the five main unions
OL,14,Fin the sector, accepted a 5.5% pay
OL,15,Foffer for 2024/25, ending their
OL,16,Fongoing industrial action.
