OL,6,FNASUWT general secretary Matt Wrack
OL,7,Fsaid the settlement is a "fair
OL,8,Foutcome" for teachers that
OL,9,F"demonstrates what can be achieved
OL,10,Fthrough constructive negotiation, even
OL,11,Funder significant constraint".
OL,13,F"However, fair pay is only one pillar
OL,14,Fof securing the teaching profession
OL,15,Ffor the future." he said.
OL,17,F"The (Education Minister Paul Givan)
OL,18,Fmust now act with urgency to address
OL,19,Fthe other core challenge, which is the
OL,20,Fscourge of excessive workload. "
