OL,6,FIn a statement the Education Minister
OL,7,FPaul Givan welcomed the decision
OL,8,Fsaying: "Extensive work has taken
OL,9,Fplace to offer a pay increase which is
OL,10,Fin line with the increase received by
OL,11,Fteachers in England and Wales. I am
OL,12,Fpleased that the five trade unions
OL,13,Fwhich make up the Northern Ireland
OL,14,FTeachers' Council have now formally
OL,15,Faccepted this on behalf of their
OL,16,Fmembers.
