OL,6,F"The 4% pay settlement will see the
OL,7,Fstarting salary for graduate teachers
OL,8,Fincreasing to #32,916, with an
OL,9,Fexperienced teacher at the top of the
OL,10,Fupper pay scale moving to #50,876.
OL,11,FThis brings teachers in Northern
OL,12,FIreland onto broadly comparable scales
OL,13,Fto their counterparts in England and
OL,14,FWales.
