OL,4,Caccept 4% pay rise
OL,6,F"Today's pay award reflects the value
OL,7,Fthat I place on those working in
OL,8,Feducation, despite the severe
OL,9,Ffinancial issues facing education and
OL,10,Fthe wider public sector in Northern
OL,11,FIreland. It firmly demonstrates my
OL,12,Fsupport for teachers and recognises
OL,13,Fthe vital contribution they make to
OL,14,Fchildren's life chances."
OL,16,FThe Minister concluded: "In addition
OL,17,Fto recognising their value through the
OL,18,Fpay award, I also want to assure
OL,19,Fteachers that I will respond to the
OL,20,FIndependent Review on Teacher Workload
OL,21,Fwithin the coming weeks."
