OL,9,FEngland, outpaces inflation and was
OL,10,Fsecured without any detrimental
OL,11,Fconditions".
OL,13,FHe said: "With the pay issue now
OL,14,Fsettled we will be turning our full
OL,15,Fand undivided attention to workload.
