OL,6,F"Teachers need and deserve a sustained
OL,7,Freduction in their unsustainable
OL,8,Fworkloads. Progress on this agenda is
OL,9,Fnon-negotiable and will be the measure
OL,10,Fof whether we secure long-term
OL,11,Findustrial peace."
OL,13,FNational Association Of Head Teachers
OL,14,F(NAHT) Northern Ireland also voted in
OL,15,Ffavour of the pay rise and its
OL,16,Fpresident Joanne Whyte acknowledged
OL,17,Fthe Education Minister's "efforts
OL,18,Fwithin the executive to make available
OL,19,Fthe funds to provide this much-needed
OL,20,Fuplift".
